OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FEarly low cloud and mist
OL,6,Fwill soon lift to leave a fine day
OL,7,Facross the region. It will be dry,
OL,8,Falthough with fairly cloudy skies
OL,9,Fpersisting, sunshine will be hazy.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FOvernight rain should gradually clear
OL,13,Fon Thursday to leave some sunshine for
OL,14,Fthe afternoon. Largely dry and settled
OL,15,Fthereafter too, and starting to feel
OL,16,Fwarmer again in the sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
